grace and his eternal associates Srila Bhakti

496
01:00:02,089 --> 01:00:08,219
Sundar Govinda Dev-Goswami Maharaj, Srila
Bhaktivedanta Swami Prabhupad, who we revere

497
01:00:08,219 --> 01:00:27,749
