Krishna conception, but particularly through

499
01:00:37,299 --> 01:00:40,760
Mahaprabhu—and just to close with this.
So, he said, “Brahma:

500
01:00:40,760 --> 01:00:41,760
… kandarpa-koṭi-kamanīya-viśeṣa-śobhaṁ
…

501
01:00:41,760 --> 01:00:47,660
