Rupa Goswami said:

525
01:03:00,849 --> 01:03:05,429
rasoddа̄mа̄ kа̄mа̄rbuda-madhura-dhа̄mojjvala-tanur,
yatīnа̄m uttaṁsas [taraṇikara-]vidyoti-vasanaḥ

526
01:03:05,429 --> 01:03:10,009
