rasoddа̄mа̄ kа̄mа̄rbuda-madhura-dhа̄mo

530
01:03:22,549 --> 01:03:24,539
…
(Śrīla Rūpa Goswāmī. Śrī Caitanyāṣṭakam,

531
01:03:24,539 --> 01:03:28,349
4)
How sweet and irresistible is the form of

532
01:03:28,349 --> 01:03:33,019
